name: Colorviento - Quarantine vibes #2
description:
This is my friend Belen with her lovely sweet tooth cat. I miss her so much, so I made this portrait to cheer us up. It's been 2 years ago since I've drawn her, and now she became a mother! I'm so proud of her. 
.
.
I've drawn a lot of women in their interior spaces. I made them smile, so we can feel a little bit closer.
